snippet.title: Chinny
snippet.description:
This channel goes over the many social issues of life. With the over exposure of 4th wave feminism, men's rights and issues are sometimes buried in the ground. Mentioning this is apparently "undermining the feminist movement", however that in itself is a double standard. Taking the red pill will define how you see things and call out these double standards - all for the purpose of justice, help others, understadning and hopefully self improvement.

I was a Fortnite World Cup Qualifier Finalist.
